item.title: Residential Subscription: Flower Arrangement
item.dc:creator: vonhan
item.description: Bring fresh air to your life with our residential subscription offering. Our custom designs are offered bi-weekly or monthly. Each week a custom design is made with the season’s best, fresh blooms. Containers will vary. The photo image is a general aesthetic of the arrangement you will receive. The overall quality and design of our arrangements will always be to Scotts’ standards.
